\id EZR 15 
\h Izira Maxaafaa 
\toc1 Izira Maxaafaa 
\toc2 Izira Maxaafaa 
\toc3 Izira Maxaafaa 
\mt1 Izira Maxaafaa  
\is1 Gidduwaa Erissuwaa  
\ip Izira Maxaafai Hanidabaa Odiya naa77u maxaafata kaalliyaagaa. Ha maxaafai Aihudatuppe omoodettidi biida amarida asati Baabilooneppe simmidoogaanne Yerusalaamen asaassi de7oikka goinoikka ooraxxidoogaa odees. Ha hanotati hagaappe kaallidi xaafettidosona.  
\io1 1. Omooduwan biida Aihudatuppe Parsse Kawuwaa Qiiroosa sheniyan koiro simmiyaageeti Baabilooneppe simmidosona.  
\io1 2. Beeta Maqidasee wotti yegetti keexettidi anjjettiis. Xoossaassi goinniyoogeekka wotti yegettidi doomettiis.  
\io1 3. Issi amarida wodiyaappe simmin, Xoossaa higgiyaa loittidi eriya Iziri kaalettin, hara Aihudati Yerusalaame simmidosona. Iziri Israa7eela asaa ayyaanaa de7uwaa kase sohuwaa zaaranau, asai ayyaanaa de7uwaanne issippetettaa de7uwaa wotti yeggidi minttanaadan maaddiis.  
\c 1  
\s1 Aihuda Asai Bantta Biittau Simmana Mala Qiiroosi Awaajjiis  
\p
\v 1 Parsse Kawoi Qiiroosi kawotido koiro laittan, hananabaa yootiya Ermmaasa baggaara GODAI haasayidobaa poliis. Parsse Kawoi Qiiroosi ba kawotettaa giddon ubbasan hagaadan yaagidi awaajjanaadaaninne xaafidi wottanaadan GODAI a ayyaanaa denttettiis;  
\v 2 “Parsse Kawoi Qiiroosi hagaadan yaagees; ‘GODAI, saluwaa Xoossai ha sa7aa kawotettata ubbaa taayyo immiis; qassi Yihudan de7iya Yerusalaamen taani ayyo Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxanaadan tana sunttiis.  
\v 3 Xoossaa asa gidida ooninne yaa bo. A Xoossai aara gido! Intte Yihudan de7iya Yerusalaame biidi, yan Yerusalaamen de7iya GODAA, Israa7eela Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa zaarettidi keexxite.  
\v 4 Dumma dumma biittan de7iya asai ubbai Aihudatuppe attidaageetuyyo biraa, worqqaa, dumma dumma miishshatanne mehiyaa immidi maaddona; qassi Yerusalaamen de7iya Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaassikka bantta dosan immiyo imotaa immona’ yaagiis” yaagees.   
\p
\v 5 Hegaappe guyyiyan, Yihudaa zaretunne Biniyaama zaretu halaqati, qeesetinne Leewati, qassi Xoossai eta wozanaa denttettido ubbati Yerusalaamen GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxanau baanau denddidosona.  
\v 6 Qassi eta shooron de7iyaageetikka bantta dosan immidobaa bolli gujjidi, bira miishshaanne worqqa miishshaa, hara dumma dumma miishshatanne mehiyaa immidi, eta maaddidosona.  
\v 7 Hegaa bollikka qassi Kawoi Qiiroosi Naabukadanaxoori Yerusalaameppe efiidi ba xoossatu keettan wottido GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyaa miishshata immiis.  
\v 8 Immin Parsse Kawoi Qiiroosi miishshata wottiyo keettaa halaqaa Mitiredaatan kesissidinne qoodissidi, Yihudaa haariya SHeshibaaxaara kushiyan sheedhdhiis.  
\v 9 Simmida miishshatu qoodai hagaa: hasttamu worqqa saineta, issi sha7u bira saineta, laatamanne uddufun billamata,  
\v 10 worqqaappe oosettida hasttamu miishshata, biraappe oosettida oiddu xeetanne tammu miishshatanne issi sha7u hara dumma dumma miishshata.  
\v 11 Worqqa miishshatunne bira miishshatu qoodai muleera ichchashu sha7anne oiddu xeeta; ha miishshata ubbaa omooduwan biida asai Baabilooneppe Yerusalaame simmiyo wode SHeshibaaxaari ekki yiis.   
\c 2  
\s1 Omooduwaappe Simmida Israa7eela Asaa Qoodaa  
\r (Nahimiyaa 7:4-73)  
\p
\v 1 Baabiloone Kawoi Naabukadanaxoori omooddidi, ba biitti efiido asaappe guyye bantta katamaa katamaa, Yerusalaamenne Yihudaa simmida asati hagaappe kaalliyaageeta.  
\v 2 Eta halaqati Zarubaabeela, Yaasa, Nahimiyaa, Saraaya, Ra7eelaaya, Marddikiyoosa, Bilishaana, Misppaara, Bigiwaaya, Rehuumanne Ba7aana.  
\p Omooduwaappe simmida Israa7eela asaa qoodai hagaa.   
\p
\v 3 Par77oosha yarati 2,172.   
\m
\v 4 SHafaaxiyaa yarati 372.   
\m
\v 5 Araaha yarati 775.   
\m
\v 6 Yaasunne Yoo7aaba naata gidiya Paahati-Moo7aaba yarati 2,812.   
\m
\v 7 Elaama yarati 1,254.   
\m
\v 8 Zattu yarati 945.   
\m
\v 9 Zakkaaya yarati 760.   
\m
\v 10 Baana yarati 642.   
\m
\v 11 Bebaaya yarati 623.   
\m
\v 12 Azggaada yarati 1,222.   
\m
\v 13 Adooniqaama yarati 666.   
\m
\v 14 Bigiwaaya yarati 2,056.   
\m
\v 15 Adiina yarati 454.   
\m
\v 16 Hizqqiyaasa yara gidiya Axeera yarati 98.   
\m
\v 17 Bexaaya yarati 323.   
\m
\v 18 Yoora yarati 112.   
\m
\v 19 Hashuuma yarati 223.   
\m
\v 20 Gibbaara yarati 95.   
\m
\v 21 Beetaliheeme asai 123.   
\m
\v 22 Naxoofa katamaa asai 56.   
\m
\v 23 Anatoota katamaa asai 128.   
\m
\v 24 Azimaaweeta katamaa asai 42.   
\m
\v 25 Qiriyaati-Yi7aariima, Kafiiranne Ba7eroota katamatu asai 743.   
\m
\v 26 Raamanne Gebaa7a katamatu asai 621.   
\m
\v 27 Mikimaasa katamaa asai 122.   
\m
\v 28 Beeteelenne Aaya katamatu asai 223.   
\m
\v 29 Nabo katamaa asai 52.   
\m
\v 30 Maagibiisha katamaa asai 156.   
\m
\v 31 Naa77antto Elaama katamaa asai 1,254.   
\m
\v 32 Hariima katamaa asai 320.   
\m
\v 33 Looda, Hadiidanne Oono katamatu asai 725.   
\m
\v 34 Yarkko katamaa asai 345.   
\m
\v 35 Sanaa7a katamaa asai 3,630.   
\m
\v 36 Hageeti omooduwaappe simmida qeeseta:  
\m Yaasu yara gidiya Yadaaya yarati 973;   
\m
\v 37 Imeera yarati 1,052;   
\m
\v 38 Paashihuura yarati 1,247;   
\m
\v 39 Hariima yarati 1,017.   
\p
\v 40 Hageeti omooduwaappe simmida Leewata:  
\m Hodaawiyaa yara gidiya Yaasunne Qaadimi7eela yarati 74;   
\m
\v 41 Asaafa yara gidiya mazamuriyaa yexxiyaageeti 128;   
\m
\v 42 Beeta Maqidasiyaa penggiyaa naagiya SHaaluuma, Axeera, Xalmmoona, Aqquuba, Haxiixanne SHobaaya yarati 139.   
\p
\v 43 Hageeti omooduwaappe simmidi, Beeta Maqidasiyan oottiya ashkkaratu yarata: Xiiha yarata, Hasuufa yarata, Xabba7oota yarata,  
\v 44 Qeeroosa yarata, Si7aaha yarata, Padoona yarata,  
\v 45 Labaana yarata, Hagaaba yarata, Aqquuba yarata,  
\v 46 Hagaaba yarata, SHamilaaya yarata, Hanaana yarata,  
\v 47 Giddeela yarata, Gahaara yarata, Ra7aaya yarata,  
\v 48 Raaxiina yarata, Naqoda yarata, Gazzaama yarata,  
\v 49 Uzza yarata, Paaseeha yarata, Besaaya yarata,  
\v 50 Asina yarata, Me7uniima yarata, Nafisiima yarata,  
\v 51 Baaqibuuqa yarata, Haquufa yarata, Harihuura yarata,  
\v 52 Baaxiluuta yarata, Mahiida yarata, Harshsha yarata,  
\v 53 Barqqoosa yarata, Sisaara yarata, Temaaha yarata,  
\v 54 Naxiiha yaratanne Haxiifa yarata.   
\p
\v 55 Hageeti omooduwaappe simmida Solomona ashkkaratu yarata: Soxaaya yarata, Hassofereeta yarata, Paruuda yarata,  
\v 56 Yaa7ila yarata, Darqqoona yarata, Giddeela yarata,  
\v 57 SHafaaxiyaa yarata, Haxxiila yarata, Pokereti-Haxxabaima yaratanne Aama yarata.  
\v 58 Omooduwaappe simmidi, Beeta Maqidasiyan oottiya ashkkaratu yaratunne Solomona ashkkaratu yaratu qoodai muleera heezzu xeetanne uddufun tammanne naa77a.   
\p
\v 59 Haratikka qassi Telmmelaaha, Teliharshsha, Karuuba, Adaananne Imeera giyo katamatuppe Yerusalaame simmidosona. SHin eti woikko eta aawati Israa7eela sheeshsha gidiyoogaa erissanau eti danddayibookkona.  
\v 60 Hegeeti Dalaaya, Xoobbiyaanne Naqoda yarata; eta qoodaikka muleera usuppun xeetanne ishatamanne naa77a.   
\p
\v 61 Qeesetuppe qassi Habaaya yarati, Haqqooxa yaratinne Barzzillaaya yarati simmidosona. Hagee Barzzillaaya giyoogee Gala7aade biitta asa gidiya Barzzillaaya na7iyo machchidi, ba bolluwaa sunttaa ekkiis.  
\v 62 Hageeti bantta yeleta xaphuwaa eranau yeletaa maxaafan koyidosona, shin demmibookkona. Hegaa gishshau, eti tunadan qoodettidi, qeesetettan oottennaadan digettidosona.  
\v 63 Qassi Uriimiyaaninne Tumiimiyan shaakkidi pirddiya qeesee denddana gakkanaashin, eti geeshsha qumaappe maanau danddayennaagaa Aihudata haariyaagee etau yootiis.   
\p
\v 64 Omooduwaappe Yihudaa biittaa simmida asaa qoodai muleera 42,360.  
\v 65 Hegaa bollikka qassi 7,337 attuma ashkkaratinne macca ashkkaratinne 200 attumanne macca mazamuriyaa yexxiyaageetikka simmidosona.  
\v 66 Omooduwaappe muleera simmida asaa paratu qoodai 736; baquloti 245;  
\v 67 gaameelati 435; hareti qassi 6,720.   
\p
\v 68 Eti Yerusalaamen kase GODAA Beeta Maqidasee de7iyo sohuwaa gakkido wode, yaratu halaqatuppe amaridaageeti GODAA Beeta Maqidasee kase ba sohuwan keexettana mala, bantta dosan imotaa immidosona.  
\v 69 Issoi issoi bau danddayiyoogaa keenaa keenaa ha Beeta Maqidasiyaa oosuwaassi immiis; eti muleera 500 kilo giraame deexxiya worqqaa, 2,800 kilo giraame deexxiya biraanne 100 qeesetu maayuwaa immidosona.   
\p
\v 70 Hegaappe guyyiyan qeeseti, Leewatinne asaappe amaridaageeti Yerusalaamen uttidosona; mazamuriyaa yexxiyaageeti, Beeta Maqidasiyaa penggiyaa naagiyaageetinne Beeta Maqidasiyan oottiya ashkkarati Yerusalaame yuushuwan de7iya katamatun uttidosona; qassi attida asati ubbai bantta katamatun katamatun uttidosona.   
\c 3  
\s1 Kase Eti Goinniyo Wogaa Zaaretti Doommidosona  
\p
\v 1 Israa7eela asai bantta kataman kataman woppu giidi uttidosona. Hegaappe guyyiyan, laappuntta aginai gakkiyo wode, eti ubbai issi asadan Yerusalaamen shiiqidosona.  
\v 2 SHiiqin Yoxedeeqa na7aa Yaasunne aara oottiya qeeseti qassi Salaatiyaala na7aa Zarubaabeelinne a dabboti Xoossaa asaa Muuse higgiyan kase xaafettidoogaadan xuuggiyo yarshshuwaa yarshshanau, Israa7eela Xoossaayyo yarshshiyoosaa giigissidosona.  
\v 3 Eti he biittan de7iya asau yayyikkonne, aggennan yarshshuwaa yarshshiyoosaa kase i kolettido man77iyan zaarettidi keexxidosona. Keexxi giigissidi, xuuggiyo yarshshuwaa GODAASSI maalladonne omarssi ubba wode yarshshidosona.  
\v 4 Kase xaafettidoogaadankka eti Daase Baalaa bonchchidosona; xuuggiyo yarshshuwaakka hachchissi hachchissi bessiyaagaa qoodaa pacissennan yarshshidosona.  
\v 5 Qassi ubba wode yarshshiyo xuuggiyo yarshshuwaa, aginai xeeriyo wode yarshshiyo yarshshuwaanne GODAA geeshsha baalatun yarshshiyo yarshsho ubbaakka yarshshidosona. Hegaa bollikka asai ba dosan GODAASSI immido imota ubbaakka yarshshidosona.  
\v 6 Laappuntta aginan koiro gallassan eti GODAAYYO xuuggiyo yarshshuwaa yarshshiyoogaa doommidosona; shin he wode GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxiyo baasoi biron baasettiichchibeenna.   
\s1 Beeta Maqidasiyaa Zaaretti Keexxiyoogaa Doommidosona  
\p
\v 7 Hegaappe guyyiyan, shuchchaa massiyaageetussinne anaaxetussi miishshaa qanxxidi qaxaridosona. Parsse Kawoi Qiiroosi etau azazido gishshau, Liibaanoosappe zigaa abbaa pinttidi, Yoophphe ehaanau Sidoonanne Xiiroosa biittaa asau qumaa, ushshaanne zaitiyaa immidosona.   
\p
\v 8 Hegaappe guyyiyan, eti Yerusalaamen de7iya GODAA Beeta Maqidasee de7iyo sohuwaa gakkido naa77antto laittan naa77antto aginan, Salaatiyaala na7ai Zarubaabeeli, Yoxedeeqa na7aa Yaasunne eta dabboti, qeeseti, Leewatinne omooduwaappe simmidi, Yerusalaame yiida asai ubbai oosuwaa doommidosona. Qassi GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyaa oosuwaa aawatettan xeellana mala, laatamu laitta gididoogeetanne laatamu laittappe aadhdhido Leewata sunttidosona.  
\v 9 Leewa zare gidiya Yaasu, a naatinne a dabboti, Hodaawiyaa yara gidiya Qaadimi7eelinne a naati issippe gididi, GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyaa oosuwaa aawatettan xeellidosona; qassi Henadaada yara gidiya Leewatikka eta maaddidosona.   
\p
\v 10 Anaaxeti GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxanau baasuwaa baasidi wurssido wode, qeeseti bantta maayuwaa maayidinne xurumbbaa oiqqidi, qassi Asaafa yara gidiya, Leewatikka, daalaa oiqqidi, Israa7eela Kawuwaa Daawita wogaadan GODAA galatanau eqqidosona.  
\v 11 Eti GODAA galatiiddinne kayan kayan mazamuriyan sabbiiddi, hagaadan yaagidi, au yexxidosona;  
\q1 “GODAI keha;  
\q2 i Israa7eela siiqiyo aggenna siiqoi merinaagaa” yaagidosona.  
\m Qassi GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyaa baasoi baasettido gishshau, asai ubbai bantta qaalaa xoqqu oottidi hombbociiddi, GODAA galatidosona.  
\v 12 SHin kase Beeta Maqidasiyaa be7ida cima qeesetuppe, Leewatuppenne zaretu halaqatuppe daroti ha77i Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxanau baasettida baasuwaa be7ido wode, bantta qaalaa xoqqu oottidi yeekkidosona; harati mati ufaittidi hombbocidosona.  
\v 13 Hegaa gishshau, ufaittidi hombbociyaagaa yeekkiyaagaappe shaakkidi eranau danddayettibeenna. Aissi giikko, eti keehippe wocamiyo gishshau, eta wocamaikka haahosan siyettees.   
\c 4  
\s1 Beeta Maqidasiyaa Zaaridi Keexxenna Mala Digganau Denddidaageeta  
\p
\v 1 Omooduwaappe simmida asati GODAASSI, Israa7eela Xoossaassi Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxiyoogaa Yihudaanne Biniyaama morkketi siyidosona.  
\v 2 Siyidi, Zarubaabeelakkonne zaretu halaqatukko yiidi, hagaadan yaagidosona; “Asoore Kawoi Asiraadooni\f 1 \fr 4:2 \fk Asiraadooni: \ft  Ibraawettuwan “Esar-Haddon” geetettees. Kawotu Maxaafaa Naa77anttuwaa 19:37 xeella.\f* nuna ha sohuwau ehiido gallassaappe doommidi, nuunikka intte Xoossaayyo yarshshoosinne ayyo goinnoos. Hegaa gishshau, nuunikka inttenaara issippe ane keexxoos” yaagidosona.   
\p
\v 3 SHin Zarubaabeeli, Yaasunne Israa7eela zaretu halaqati etayyo zaaridi, hagaadan yaagidosona; “Nu Xoossaassi Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxanau nuuyyoonne intteyyo aiba issippetettinne baawa. SHin Parsse Kawoi Qiiroosi azazidoogaadan, nu xalaalai GODAASSI Israa7eela Xoossaassi Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxana” yaagidosona.   
\p
\v 4 Hegaappe guyyiyan, Yihudaa biittaa asati Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxennaadan, he biittan de7iya asati hashiyaa sho7idosonanne yashissidosona.  
\v 5 Qassi Parsse Kawuwaa Qiiroosa laittai wuranaashiininne appe simmin Daariyoosi\f 2 \fr 4:5 \fk Daariyoosi: \ft  Daariyoosa taarikee paiduwaa 24ppe doommidi xaafettiis. Paiduwaa 6-23 gakkanau xaafettida taarikee Beeta Maqidasee keexettoosappe issi xeetu laitta gidiyaagaa gam77in hanidabaa.\f* Parssen kawotido wodee gakkanaashin, eti Yihudaa asatu zoretaa laalanau zorettiyaageeta miishshan qaxaridosona.   
\s1 Yerusalaamee Naa77anttuwaa Keexettennaadan Digettiis  
\p
\v 6 Hegaappe guyyiyan, Arxxekssiisi kawotaa doommiyoorin, eti Yihudaanne Yerusalaame asaa mootanau pailiyaa dooyidosona.   
\p
\v 7 Qassi simmidi, Arxxekssiisi kawotiiddi de7ishin, Bishilaami, Mitiredaati, Xaabi7eelinne eta yarati issippe gididi, Parsse Kawuwaa Arxxekssiisau dabddaabbiyaa xaafidosona; he dabddaabbee Sooriyaa biittaa pitaliyaaninne qaalan xaafettiis.   
\p
\v 8 Biittaa haariya Rehuuminne xaafiyaa SHimshshaayi Yerusalaamebaa hagaadan yaagidi, Kawuwaa Arxxekssiisau dabddaabbiyaa xaafidosona;  
\v 9 “Ha dabddaabbee biittaa haariya Rehuumappe, xaafiyaa SHimshshaayappe, beni Elaama biittan de7iya Suusappe, Ereekappenne Baabilooneppe yiida pirddiyaanne daannatiyaa eta yaratuppenne  
\v 10 gitanne bonchchettida Kawuwaa Asanaafari\f 3 \fr 4:10 \fk Asanaafari: \ft  Ibraawettuwan “Osnappar” geetettees. Ha kawoi qassi “Assurbanipal” geetettees.\f* omooddi ehiidi, Samaariyaaninne Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittan wottido asa ubbaappe xaafettiis” yaagidosona.   
\p
\v 11 Eti ayyo kiittido dabddaabbee hagaadan yaagees; “Kawuwaa Arxxekssiisau, Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittan de7iya ne ashkkaratuppe:   
\p
\v 12 “Kawuwau, ne matappe haa nuukko yiida Aihudati Yerusalaame biidi, he makkalanchchanne iita katamaa zaaridi keexxiiddi de7iyoogaa era. A gimbbiyaa ooraxissoosona; a xaphuwaakka bottokonoosona.  
\v 13 Qassi kawuwau, ha katamai keexettiyaabaa gidikkonne a gimbbiyaakka ooraxissiyaabaa gidikko, hegaappe guyyiyan, eti giiraanne qaraxaa qanxxennaagaa era. Hegaappe denddidaagan kawo keettau geliya miishshai paca gidana.  
\v 14 Nuuni kawoi sunttin oottiyaageeta gidiyo gishshaunne kawoi kauyyishin be7anau koyenna gishshau, hagaa neeni erana mala giidi kiittoos.  
\v 15 Hegaa gishshau, kase ne aawatu taarikiyaa maxaafai koyettidi xeeletto; hegan xaafettidabaappe neeni ha katamai beniisappekka doommidi, makkalanchcha katama gidiyoogaanne kawotussinne biittatussi metuwaa medhdhidaagaa gidiyoogaa eranau danddayaasa. Hegaappe denddidaagan i kolettiis.  
\v 16 Hegaa gishshau, ha katamai keexettiyaabaa gidikkonne a gimbbiyaakka ooraxissiyaabaa gidikko, Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittai ne kushiyaappe kiyidoogaa era” yaagidosona.   
\p
\v 17 Kawoi hagaadan yaagiya zaaruwaa etayyo yeddiis; “Biittaa haariya Rehuumaa, xaafiyaa SHimshshaayaa, Samaariyaaninne Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittan de7iya eta yara gidiya asa ubbau, inttena saro gais.  
\v 18 Intte taayyo yeddido dabddaabbee birshshettidi nabbabettiis.  
\v 19 Taani azazin, kase taarikee koyettidi xeelettiis; xeelettiyo wode, ha katamai beniisappekka doommidi, kawotussi makkalanchcha gidiyoogeenne metuwaa medhdhiyaageeti de7iyo soho gidiyoogee erettiis.  
\v 20 Yerusalaamen wolqqaama kawoti kawotidosona; Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittaappekka he kawoti giiraanne qaraxaa ekkidosona.  
\v 21 Hegaa gishshau, taani etayyo oottite giyo azazuwaa immana gakkanaashin, ha asati he katamaa keexxiyoogaa essana mala odite.  
\v 22 Intte ha yohuwaa shenehoo geennaadan naagettite. Aissi giikko, kawotuyyo metuwaa darissanau koshshenna” yaagidi kiittiis.   
\p
\v 23 Kawuwaa Arxxekssiisa dabddaabbee Rehuumassi, xaafiyaa SHimshshaayassinne eta yara gidiya ubbatussi nabbabettido wode, Yerusalaamen de7iya Aihuda asatukko eesotiiddi biidi, eti keexxiyoogaa wolqqan teqqidosona.   
\p
\v 24 Teqqin Yerusalaamen de7iya Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa oosoi Daariyoosi kawotido naa77antto laittai gakkanaashin, eqqosan atti aggiis.   
\c 5  
\s1 Beeta Maqidasiyaa Oosoi Naa77anttuwaa Doomettiis  
\p
\v 1 He wodiyan hananabaa yootiya Haggeenne Iddo na7ai Zakkaariyaasi Yihudaaninne Yerusalaamen de7iya Aihuda asatuyyo Israa7eela Xoossaa sunttan hananabaa yootidosona.  
\v 2 Salaatiyaala na7ai Zarubaabeelinne Yoxedeeqa na7ai Yaasu denddidi, Yerusalaamen de7iya GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyaa zaarettidi keexxanau doommidosona. Hananabaa yootiyaageetikka etaara issippe gididi, eta maaddidosona.   
\p
\v 3 He wode, Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittaa haariya Tattanaaya giyoogee, SHatarbbozina giyoogeenne etaara oottiyaageeti yiidi, “Intte ha Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxana malanne polana mala, intteyyo oonee odidai?” yaagidi oichchidosona.  
\v 4 Eti qassi, “Ha Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxiya asatu sunttai oonee oonee?” yaagidikka oichchidosona.  
\v 5 SHin he yohoi Daariyoosakko gakkin, a matappe dabddaabbee xaafettidi yaana gakkanaashin, eti bantta oosuwaa aggibookkona; aissi giikko, eta Xoossaa aifee Yihudaa biittaa cimatu bollan de7ees.   
\p
\v 6 Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittaa haariya Tattanaayi, SHatarbbozininne etaara oottiyaageeti Kawuwaa Daariyoosayyo kiittido dabddaabbee  
\v 7 hagaadan yaagees;  
\p “Kawuwaa Daariyoosaa, kumetta sarotettai neeyyo gido!   
\p
\v 8 “Nuuni Yihudaa biittan de7iya gita Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaakko biida. He Beeta Maqidasee gita shuchchan keexettiis; qassi gimbbiyaa bollankka mittai wodhdhiis. Oosoikka gita akeekaaninne eesuwan oosettiiddi de7ees.   
\p
\v 9 “Eta kaalettiya cimata nuuni hagaadan yaagidi oichchida; ‘Ha Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxana malanne polana mala, intteyyo oonee odidai?’ yaagidi oichchida.  
\v 10 Qassi neeyyo xaafidi erissana mala, eta ha oosuwan kaalettiyaageetu sunttaikka oonakko oichchida.   
\p
\v 11 “Oichchin, eti hagaadan yaagidi zaaridosona; ‘Nuuni saluwaanne sa7aa Xoossaa ashkkarata; qassi nuuni Israa7eela kawuwaa gitai daro laittaappe kase baggan keexxi polido Beeta Maqidasiyaa zaaretti keexxeettees.  
\v 12 Nu aawati saluwaa Xoossaa hanqqetissido gishshau, i eta Baabiloone Kawuwaa Naabukadanaxoora kushiyan aatti immiis. Immin, i ha Beeta Maqidasiyaa koli aggiis; asaakka Baabiloone biitti omooduwau ekkidi biis.   
\p
\v 13 “‘SHin Baabiloone Kawoi Qiiroosi ba kawotido koiro laittan, Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa, hagaa zaaretti keexxana mala, awaajuwaa kessiis.  
\v 14 Naabukadanaxoori Yerusalaamen de7iya Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaappe ekki efiidi, Baabiloone biittan de7iya ba xoossatu keettan wottido worqqanne bira miishshatakka Qiiroosi zaaridi yeddiis.  
\p “‘He miishshati Kawoi Qiiroosi Yihudaa biittaa haarana mala doorido SHeshibaaxaara kushiyan sheerettidosona.  
\v 15 SHeedhdhiiddi Kawoi Qiiroosi a hagaadan yaagiis; “Ha miishshata ekka efaada Yerusalaamen de7iya Beeta Maqidasiyan wotta; qassi Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaakka kase i de7iyo sohuwan keexxa” yaagiis.  
\v 16 Hegaappe guyyiyan, SHeshibaaxaari yiidi, Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxiyo sohuwaa Yerusalaamen baasiis. I ha77ikka wuribeennaagaa gidikkonne, he wodeesappekka doommidi, keexettiiddi de7ees’ yaagidosona.   
\p
\v 17 “Ha77i simmi ha yohoi kawuwaa ufaissiyaabaa gidikko, ane Kawoi Qiiroosi ha Beeta Maqidasiyaa Yerusalaamen keexxana mala, tumukka awaajuwaa kessidaakko eranau kase aadhdhida Baabiloone kawotu taarikiyaa mazggafai koyettidi xeeletto. Hegaappe guyyiyan, kawoi nuuni ha yohuwaa waatanau bessiyaakko qachchido qofaa nuuyyo kiitto” yaagidi xaafidosona.   
\c 6  
\s1 Qiiroosi Kase Azazido Azazoi Koyettidi Beettiis  
\p
\v 1 Hegaa gishshau, Kawoi Daariyoosi azazin, Baabiloone miishshata wottiyo keettan de7iya taarikiyaa mazggafata eti koyidosona.  
\v 2 SHin Baabiloone kataman gidennan de7ishin, Meedoona biittan de7iya Ahimtta\f 4 \fr 6:2 \fk Ahimtta: \ft Ha katamai qassi Ekibataana geetettees.\f* giyo kataman issi xaatta maxaafai beettiis. He maxaafan xaafettidabai hagaadan yaagees;   
\p
\v 3 “Wodenau dogettennaadan, Kawoi Qiiroosi ba kawotido koiro laittan, Yerusalaamen de7iya Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa gishshau, hagaadan yaagiya awaajuwaa kessiis; ‘Yerusalaamen de7iya Xoossaa Beeta Maqidase gidiya, Aihudati yarshshuwaa yarshshiyo sohoi zaarettidi keexetto; a baasoikka baasetto. He Beeta Maqidasee usuppun tammu wara adussanne usuppun tammu wara aaho gido.  
\v 4 Qassi heezzu maaran gita shuchchai wodhdhin, he maaratu bollan bollaara issi maara mittai wodhdho. Hegau koshshiya miishshai ubbai kawo keettan buquraa wottiyo keettaappe imetto.  
\v 5 Naabukadanaxoori Yerusalaamen de7iya Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaappe ekkidi, Baabiloone ehiido Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa worqqanne bira miishshati bantta sohuwau guyye Yerusalaame simmona; simmidi Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyan de7ona’ yaagiis” yaagees.   
\p
\v 6 Hegaappe guyyiyan, Daariyoosi xaafido dabddaabbee hagaadan yaagees; “Inttenoo Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittaa haariya Tattanaayaa, SHatarbbozinaanne etaara oottiya ubbatoo, he Beeta Maqidasiyaakko shiiqoppite.  
\v 7 Ha asati keexxiyo Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa oosuwaassi xube gidoppite. Aihudata haariyaageenne Aihuda cimati Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa kase i de7iyo sohuwan zaaridi keexxona.   
\p
\v 8 “Qassi ha Aihuda cimati Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxiyo wode, eti oottiyo oosoi eqqenna mala, etassi koshshiya miishshaa ubbaa Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittaappe shiishshido kawuwaa giiraa miishshaappe intte etayyo immana mala, taani azazaas.  
\v 9 Yerusalaamen de7iya qeeseti saluwaa Xoossaassi xuuggiyo yarshshuwaa yarshshanau koshshiyaabai mirggota gidin, dorssa orggeta gidin woikko qassi dorssa marata gidikkokka etayyo immite. Qassi aibanne pacissennan eti koyiyo gisttiyaa, maxiniyaa, woiniyaa eessaanne zaitiyaa etayyo hachchi hachchi immite.  
\v 10 Hegaa intte immiyoogee eti saluwaa Xoossaa keehi ufaissiya yarshshuwaa yarshshanaassanne kawuwaanne kawuwaa naatu de7uwaa gishshaukka woossanaassa.   
\p
\v 11 “Ha awaajuwaa laammiya ooninne de7ikko, ‘A keettaa tuussaa shoddidi, he tuussaa xeeraa pooxidoogan lukettidi haiqqo; a keettaikka pito oliyo soho gido’ gaada gujjadakka azazaas.  
\v 12 Ha azazuwaa laammanaunne qassi Yerusalaamen de7iya Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa kolanau kushiyaa denttiya ai kawo woi dere gidin, ba sunttai xeesettana mala Yerusalaame doorida Xoossai a xaisso. Taani Daariyoosi hagaa azazaas. Ha yohuwaa asai ubbai minotettan polo” yaagees.   
\s1 Beeta Maqidasiyaa Anjjissiyo Baalaa  
\p
\v 13 Hegaappe guyyiyan, Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittaa haariya Tattanaayi, SHatarbbozininne etaara oottiya ubbati Kawoi Daariyoosi azazidoogaadan minotettan oottidi polidosona.  
\v 14 Hegaa gishshau, Aihuda cimati bantta oosuwaa aggennan oottidosona; qassi hananabaa yootiya Haggeenne Iddo na7ai Zakkaariyaasi yootido qaalankka minettidosona. Israa7eela Xoossai azazidoogaadaaninne Parsse biittaa kawoti Qiiroosi, Daariyoosinne Arxxekssiisi awaajjidoogaadan Beeta Maqidasee keexettidi wuriis.  
\v 15 Daariyoosi kawotido usuppuntta laittan Adaare giyo aginan heezzantto gallassan, Beeta Maqidasiyaa oosoi polettiis.   
\p
\v 16 Hegaappe guyyiyan, Israa7eela asai, qeeseti, Leewatinne omooduwaappe simmida asai ubbai Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa anjjissiyo baalaa ufaissan bonchchidosona.  
\v 17 He baalaa bonchchiyo wode, eti issi xeetu korimata, naa77u xeetu dorssa orggetanne oiddu xeetu dorssa marata yarshshidosona; qassi nagaraa yarshshuwaassi tammanne naa77u Israa7eela zaretu qoodan tammanne naa77u deeshsha orggetakka yarshshidosona.  
\v 18 Muuse Maxaafan xaafettidoogaadan, Yerusalaamen de7iya Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyan oottana mala, qeesetanne Leewata eta maaraadan maaraadan wottidosona.   
\s1 Paasikaa Baalaa  
\p
\v 19 Omooduwaappe simmida asati kaalliya laittan koiro aginan tammanne oiddantto gallassan Paasikaa Baalaa bonchchidosona.  
\v 20 Qassi qeesetinne Leewati banttana geeshshidosona; hegaa gishshau, eti ubbaikka geeshsha. Hegaappe guyyiyan, Leewati omooduwaappe simmida ubbaayyo, qeesetuyyoonne bantta huuphiyau Paasikaa dorssaa shukkidosona.  
\v 21 SHukkin, omooduwaappe simmida Israa7eela asainne Aihuda gidenna asati oottiyo tunatettaappe banttana shaakkidi, GODAAKKO, Israa7eela Xoossaakko simmida asai ubbai Paasikaa miidosona.  
\v 22 Qassi eti laappun gallassau Oittaa Baalaa ufaissan bonchchidosona; aissi giikko, GODAI eta ufaissiis; qassi Xoossaa, hegeekka Israa7eela Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa eti keexxidi polana mala, Asoore kawuwaa qofaa GODAI laammin, kawoi eta maaddiis.   
\c 7  
\s1 Iziri Yerusalaame Yiis  
\p
\v 1 Hegaappe simmin, daro wodiyaappe guyyiyan, Parsse biittan Arxxekssiisi kawotido wodiyan Izira giyo issi asi de7iis. I Saraaya na7aa; Saraayi Azaariyaa na7aa; Azaaree Hilqqiyaa na7aa; Hilqqee SHaaluuma na7aa;  
\v 2 SHaaluumi Xaadooqa na7aa; Xaadooqi Ahixuuba na7aa; Ahixuubi Amaariyaa na7aa;  
\v 3 Amaaree Azaariyaa na7aa; Azaaree Maraayoota na7aa; Maraayooti Zaraahiyaa na7aa;  
\v 4 Zaraahee Uzza na7aa; Uzzi Buuqa na7aa;  
\v 5 Buuqi Abishuu7a na7aa; Abishuu7i Piinihaasa na7aa; Piinihaasi El77aazara na7aa; El77aazari qeese ubbatu halaqaa Aaroona na7aa.   
\p
\v 6 Iziri Baabilooneppe yiis. I GODAI, Israa7eela Xoossai immido Muuse Higgiyaa loitti xanna7ida eranchcha asa. GODAA a Xoossaa kushee a bollan de7iyo gishshau, i oichchidobaa ubbaa kawoi ayyo immiis.  
\v 7 Israa7eela asaappe amaridaageetinne qassi qeesetuppe, Leewatuppe, mazamuriyaa yexxiyaageetuppe, penggiyaa naagiyaageetuppenne Beeta Maqidasiyaa ashkkaratuppe amaridaageeti Kawoi Arxxekssiisi kawotido laappuntta laittan Iziraara issippe Yerusalaame biidosona.  
\v 8 Kawoi kawotido laappuntta laittan ichchashantto aginan Iziri Yerusalaame gakkiis.  
\v 9 Koiro aginan koiro gallassan Baabilooneppe kiyidi, ichchashantto aginan koiro gallassan Yerusalaame gakkiis. Aissi giikko, a Xoossaa lo77o kushee a bollan de7ees.  
\v 10 Hegaa xalla gidennan Iziri GODAA Higgiyaa xanna7anaunne oottanau, qassi Israa7eela asaakka a wogaanne a pirddaa tamaarissanau ba wozanaa giigissi wottiis.   
\s1 Kawoi Arxxekssiisi Izirassi Xaafidi Immido Dabddaabbiyaa  
\p
\v 11 GODAI Israa7eelayyo immido higgiyaa xanna7idi, loitti eriya qeesenne xaafe gidiya Izirayyo Kawoi Arxxekssiisi immido dabddaabbee hagaadan yaagees;   
\p
\v 12 “Kawotu Kawuwaa Arxxekssiisappe, qeesiyaanne saluwaa Xoossaa Higgiyaa loitti xanna7iya Iziraa, saroi neeyyo gido!   
\p
\v 13 “Ta kawotettaa giddon de7iya Israa7eela asaappe ooninne, qeesetuppe woi Leewatuppe gidikkokka, Yerusalaame baanau koyiya asai ubbai nenaara issippe baanaadan taani odaas.  
\v 14 Taaninne tanaara zorettiya laappun asati issippe gididi, neeni ne kushiyan de7iya Xoossaa Higgiyaadan, baada Yihudaaninne Yerusalaamen de7iya hanotettai ai malakko oichchanaadan nena kiittoos.  
\v 15 Au de7iyo sohoi Yerusalaamen de7iyo Israa7eela Xoossaassi, taani kawoinne tanaara zorettiya asati nu dosan immido worqqaanne biraa imotata neeni ekkada ba.  
\v 16 Hegaa bollikka qassi neeni Baabiloone biittaa kumettaappe demmido biraanne worqqaa ubbaa, qassi Israa7eela asainne qeeseti Yerusalaamen de7iya bantta Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaassi bantta dosan immido imotaakka ekkada ba.  
\v 17 Baada, ha miishshan korimata, dorssa orggetanne dorssa marata, qassi kattaa yarshshuwaayyoonne ushshaa yarshshuwaayyo koshshiyaabata shammada, Yerusalaamen de7iya intte Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyan yarshshiyoosan yarshsha.   
\p
\v 18 “Hegaappe palahidi attida biraanne worqqaa neeninne nenaara de7iya ne biittaa asati oottanau koyiyoobaa intte Xoossaa sheniyaadan oottite.  
\v 19 Qassi intte Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa giddon oosettiya oosuwaassi intte go7ettana mala, nuuni neeyyo immido miishshata ubbaa Yerusalaame Xoossaa sinttan wotta.  
\v 20 Hagaappe harabai intte Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaassi koshshiyaabai aibanne gidikko, hegau koshshiya miishshaa kawo keettan miishshaa wottiyo keettaappe ekkanau danddayaasa.   
\p
\v 21 “Hegaa gishshau, ha77i taani Kawoi Arxxekssiisi Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittan de7iya miishshaa keettan aawatettai de7iyo ubbatussi ha azazuwaa immaas. Qeese gidiyaanne Saluwaa Xoossaa Higgiyaa loitti xanna7iya Iziri inttena oichchiyoobaa aiba gidikkonne ayyo immite.  
\v 22 Qassi heezzu sha7anne oiddu xeetu kilo giraame deexxiya biraa, issi xeetu kunttaale gisttiyaa, naa77u sha7u litiro woine eessaanne naa77u sha7u litiro wogaraa zaitiyaa, qassi koshshiya keena maxiniyaara ubbaa Izirayyo immite.  
\v 23 Kawuwaa bollinne kawuwaa naatu kawotettaa bolli hanqqoi yeenna mala, saluwaa Xoossai azazidobaa ubbaa saluwaa Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaassi aibanne ashshennan immite.  
\v 24 Qassi qeesetuppe, Leewatuppe, mazamuriyaa yexxiyaageetuppe, penggiyaa naagiyaageetuppe, Beeta Maqidasiyaa ashkkaratuppenne Beeta Maqidasiyaa giddon dumma dumma oosuwaa oottiya asa ubbaappe intte giiraanne qaraxaa ekkanau intteyyo aiba maatinne baawa.   
\p
\v 25 “Nenoo Iziraa, neeni qassi, neeyyo Xoossai immido aadhdhida eratettaadan Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittan de7iya ne Xoossaa Higgiyaa eriya asaa bolli pirddana mala, daannatanne pirddiyaageeta suntta. Qassi he higgiyaa erennaageeti de7ikko, eta tamaarissite.  
\v 26 Ne Xoossaa Higgiyaassinne kawuwaa higgiyaassi azazettenna ooninne de7ikko, i sohuwaarakka haiquwan, yedetan, a miishshaa bonqqiyoogan woikko qashuwan qaxxayetto” yaagees.   
\s1 Iziri GODAA Galatiis  
\p
\v 27 Yerusalaamen de7iya GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyaa hagaadan loittana mala, kawuwaa wozanan ha qofaa wottida GODAASSI, nu aawatu Xoossaassi galatai gido!  
\v 28 Qassi kawuwaa, kawuwaara zorettiyaageetunne aara oottiya wolqqaama halaqatu ubbaa sinttan ba aggenna siiquwaa taassi bessida Xoossaassi galatai gido! GODAA, ta Xoossaa kushee tanaara de7iyo gishshau, taani minettaas. Qassi Israa7eela halaqatuppe amaridaageeti tanaara simmidi, Yerusalaame baana mala shiishshaas.   
\c 8  
\s1 Iziraara Issippe Omooduwaappe Simmida Asaa  
\p
\v 1 Kawoi Arxxekssiisi kawotido wode tanaara issippe Baabiloone biittaappe simmidi, Yerusalaame yiida zaretu halaqati hageeta; eta yeletaa maaraikka hagaa:   
\q1
\v 2 Piinihaasa yaraappe Gershshooma, Itaamaara yaraappe Daaneela, Daawita yaraappe SHekaaniyaa na7aa Haxxuusha,   
\q1
\v 3 Par77oosha yaraappe Zakkaariyaasinne eta yeletaa maarai xaafettido hara issi xeetanne ishatamu attumaageeta,   
\q1
\v 4 Paahati-Moo7aaba yaraappe Zaraahiyaa na7aa Eliyoo7enaayanne aara issippe hara naa77u xeetu attumaageeta,   
\q1
\v 5 Zattu yaraappe Yahaazi7eela na7aa SHekaaniyaanne aara issippe hara heezzu xeetu attumaageeta,   
\q1
\v 6 Adiina yaraappe Yonaataana na7aa Ebeedanne aara issippe hara ishatamu attumaageeta,   
\q1
\v 7 Elaama yaraappe Ataaliyaa na7aa Yishaa7iyaanne aara issippe hara laappun tammu attumaageeta,   
\q1
\v 8 SHafaaxiyaa yaraappe Mikaa7eela na7aa Zabaadiyaanne aara issippe hara hosppun tammu attumaageeta,   
\q1
\v 9 Yoo7aaba zariyaappe Yihi7eela na7aa Obaadiyaanne aara issippe hara naa77u xeetanne tammanne hosppun attumaageeta,   
\q1
\v 10 Baana yaraappe Yosiifiyaa na7aa SHalomiitanne aara issippe hara issi xeetanne usuppun tammu attumaageeta,   
\q1
\v 11 Bebaaya yaraappe Bebaaya na7aa Zakkaariyaasanne aara issippe hara laatamanne hosppun attumaageeta,   
\q1
\v 12 Azggaada yaraappe Haqqaxaana na7aa Yohanaananne aara issippe hara issi xeetanne tammu attumaageeta,   
\q1
\v 13 Adooniqaama yaraappe wurssettan simmidaageeti, Elifeleexa, Yi7u7eela, SHamaa7iyaanne etaara issippe hara usuppun tammu attumaageetanne   
\q1
\v 14 qassi Bigiwaaya yaraappekka Utaaya, Zakkuuranne etaara issippe hara laappun tammu attumaageeta.   
\p
\v 15 Taani Iziri eta Ahaawa giyo sohuwaakko goggiya shaafaa matan shiishshaas. Nuuni he sohuwan dunkkaanidi, heezzu gallassaa takkida. Qassi taani he sohuwan de7iya asaanne qeeseta qoodiyo wode, Leewa zaretuppe issuwaanne demmabeikke.  
\v 16 Hegaa gishshau, halaqa gidiya El77eezara, Ar77eela, SHamaa7iyaa, Elnnaataana, Yaariiba, Elnnaataana, Naataana, Zakkaariyaasanne Mashulaama giyoogeetanne qassi aadhdhida eranchcha asa gidiya Yoyaariibanne Elnnaataana xeegaas.  
\v 17 Xeegada, nu Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyan oottiya asaa nuuyyo yeddana mala, Kaasifiyaa giyo sohuwan de7iya Leewatussi halaqa gidiya Iddokkonne a dabbotukko, hegeetikka Beeta Maqidasiyaa ashkkara gidiyaageetukko eta kiittaas.  
\v 18 Nu Xoossaa lo77o kushee nu bollan de7iyo gishshau, SHerebiyaa a naatuuranne a ishanttuura, muleera tammanne hosppunaa eti nuuyyo yeddidosona. I Israa7eela na7aa Leewa zare gidiya Maahila yaranne keehi akeekai de7iyo asa.  
\v 19 Qassi Hashaabiyaa, Maraara yara gidiya Yishaa7iyaara, a naatuuranne a ishanttu laatamaara yeddidosona.  
\v 20 Hegaa bollikka Leewata maaddanaadan giidi, Daawitinne aara oottiya halaqati sunttido Beeta Maqidasiyaa ashkkaratuppekka naa77u xeetanne laatamata yeddidosona. Hegeeti ubbati bantta sunttan xaafettidosona.   
\p
\v 21 Hegaappe guyyiyan, nu Xoossaa sinttan nu huuphiyaa kaushshidi, i nu ogiyan nuuyyo, nu naatuyyoonne nu aqo ubbaayyo sarotettaa immanaadan woossana mala, hegan Ahaawa SHaafaa matan taani xoomaa awaajjaas.  
\v 22 Aissi giikko, kawuwaayyo nuuni kase, “Nu Xoossaa lo77o kushee a koyiyaageetuura issippe de7ees; shin a wolqqaama hanqqoi a aggiyaageetu bollan de7ees” yaagidi yootido gishshau, nuuni biyo ogiyan de7iya morkketuppe nuna naaganaadan olanchchatanne paraasata immanaadan kawuwaa oichchanau taani yeellataas.  
\v 23 Hegaa gishshau, nuuni xoomidi, Xoossaa woossida; woossin, i nu woosaa siyiis.   
\p
\v 24 Qeesetu halaqatuppe SHerebiyaa, Hashaabiyaanne hara eta dabbo gidiya tammu asata taani dooraas.  
\v 25 Doorada, kawoi, kawuwaara zorettiyaageeti, kawuwaara oottiyaageetinne Israa7eela ubbai nu Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaassi immido biraa worqqaanne, miishshata ubbaa likkada eta kushiyan sheedhdhaas.  
\v 26 Taani etayyo immidobai hagaa: laatamanne naa77u sha7u kilo giraame deexxiya biraa, heezzu sha7anne oiddu xeetu kilo giraame deexxiya biraappe oosettida xeetu miishshata, heezzu sha7anne oiddu xeetu kilo giraame deexxiya worqqaa,  
\v 27 hosppun kilo giraamenne oiddu xeetu giraame deexxiya worqqaappe oosettida laatamu sainetanne worqqadan al77onne muruta gidida nahaasiyaappe oosettida naa77u saineta.   
\p
\v 28 Hegaappe guyyiyan, taani etayyo hagaadan yaagaas; “Inttenne ha miishshati ubbaikka GODAAYYO dummatideta; ha birainne worqqai asai ba dosan GODAAYYO, intte aawatu Xoossaayyo immidoogaa.  
\v 29 Yerusalaamen de7iya GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyan miishshaa wottiyo keettaa gakkidi, qeese halaqatu sinttan, Leewatu sinttaaninne Israa7eela zaretu halaqatu sinttan sheedhdhana gakkanaashin, ha miishshata loitti naagite” yaagaas.  
\v 30 Hegaa gishshau, qeesetinne Leewati Yerusalaamen de7iya GODAA Beeta Maqidasiyau efaanau biraa, worqqaanne hara miishshata ubbaa miizaanan likkidi sheerettidosona.   
\p
\v 31 Hegaappe guyyiyan, nuuni koiro aginan tammanne naa77antto gallassan Yerusalaame baanau Ahaawa SHaafaa mataappe denddida. Denddidi biyo wode, nu bollan de7iya nu Xoossaa lo77o kushee nu biyo ogiyan de7iya morkketuppenne panggatuppe nuna naagiisinne ashshiis.  
\v 32 Nuuni Yerusalaame gakkidi, yan heezzu gallassaa uttida.   
\p
\v 33 Oiddantto gallassi biraa, worqqaanne hara miishshata ubbaakka likkidi, Ooriyoona na7aa qeesiyaa Maremootassi sheedhdhida. Piinihaasa na7aa El77aazari, Leewa gidiya Yaasu na7aa Yozabaadinne Biinuya na7aa No7aadee aara issippe de7oosona.  
\v 34 Ubbabaikka qoodettiisinne likettiis; likettidi muleera ai keena gididaakko, he wode xaafettiis.   
\p
\v 35 Hegaappe guyyiyan, omooduwaappe simmida asai Israa7eela Xoossaassi xuuggiyo yarshshuwaa yarshshidosona. Eti Israa7eela ubbaa gishshau, tammanne naa77u korimata, uddufun tammanne usuppun dorssa orggetanne laappun tammanne laappun dorssa marata, qassi nagaraa yarshshuwaassikka tammanne naa77u deeshsha orggeta yarshshidosona. Hagee ubbai xuuggiyo yarshsho gididi, GODAAYYO shiiqiis.  
\v 36 Eti qassi kawoi azazido azazuwaakka kawuwaappe garssaara biittaa haariyaageetuyyoonne Efiraaxiisa SHaafaappe Arggo Bagga Biittaa haariyaageetuyyo immidosona; immin eti Israa7eela asaanne Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa oosuwaa maaddidosona.   
\c 9  
\s1 Aihuda Gidenna Asatuura Ekettidaageetinne Gelettidaageeti De7iyoogaa Iziri Akeekiis  
\p
\v 1 Ha ubbabai hanidoogaappe guyyiyan, asaa kaalettiyaageeti taakko yiidi, hagaadan yaagidosona; “Israa7eela asai, harai atto qeesetikka Leewatikka, bantta heeran de7iya Aihuda gidenna asatuppe banttana shaakkibookkona. Etikka Kanaaneti, Hiiteti, Parzzeti, Yaabuusati, Amoonati, Moo7aabati, Gibxxetinne Amooreti oottiyoogaadan tuna oosuwaa oottoosona.  
\v 2 Qassi banttayyoonne bantta naatuyyo Aihuda gidenna macca naatuppe machcho oottidi ekkidosona; hegaappe denddidaagan geeshsha zerettati Aihuda gidennaageetuura walakettidosona. Kaalettiyaageetinne halaqati ammanettennaageeta gididi, hagaa malabaa oottanau sintta xeera gidoosona” yaagidosona.   
\p
\v 3 Taani ha yohuwaa siyido wode, ta maayuwaanne ta qumaashshaa pooshshaas; ta huuphiyaa binnaanaanne ta buuchchaakka shoddaas; qassi daro dagammada utta aggaas.  
\v 4 Omooduwaappe simmida asai oottido nagaraa gishshau, Israa7eela Xoossai yootido qaalaassi yayyida asai ubbai taani de7iyo sohuwaa taakko shiiqiis. Omarssa yarshshuwaa yarshshiyo wodee gakkanaashinkka dagammada utto sohuwaappe taani denddabeikke.   
\p
\v 5 SHin omarssa yarshshuwaa yarshshiyo wodee gakkiyo wode, ta maayoinne ta qumaashshai pooshetti uttidaashin, taani kauyyada utto sohuwaappe denddaas. Qassi gulbbatada GODAAKKO, ta Xoossaakko, ta kushiyaa denttada, hagaadan yaagada woossaas;  
\v 6 “Abeet ta Xoossau, taani ta sinttaa neekko pude denttanaukka yayyaisinne yeellatais; aissi giikko, nu nagarai doorettidi, nu huuphiyaappe pude aadhdhiis; nu naaqoikka saluwaa gakkiis.  
\v 7 Nuuni nu maizza aawatu wodiyaappe doommidi, hachchi gakkanaashin, nena keehippe naaqqida. Nu nagaraappe denddidaagan nuuni, nu kawotinne nu qeeseti ha77iigaadankka allaga kawotu kushiyan mashshaassi, omooduwaassi, bonqqiyaassinne wurssetta yeellaassi aadhdhidi imettida.   
\p
\v 8 “SHin ha77i nuuyyo guutta maarotettaa wodee imettiis; aissi giikko, GODAI nu Xoossai nuuppe amarida zerettati attana mala oottiis; ha geeshsha sohuwan i nuna sarotettan wottiis. Nu Xoossai nu aifiyaa dooyiis; qassi nu ailletettaappekka nuuyyo ooratta de7uwaa immiis.  
\v 9 Nuuni aille gidikkonne, nu Xoossai nuna ailletettan aggibeenna; nu de7uwaa ooraxissiis. Qassi nu Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa keexxana mala, kolettidaagaa bottokonana malanne Yihudaaninne Yerusalaamen nuuni sarotettan de7ana mala, Parsse biittaa kawotu sinttan nuuyyo ba aggenna siiquwaa bessiis.   
\p
\v 10 “SHin nu Xoossau, ha77i yaatin, nuuni woiganau danddayiyoonii? Aissi giikko, nuuni ha77ikka ne azazuwaa aggiigida.  
\v 11 Hananabaa yootiya ne ashkkaratu baggaara neeni hagaadan yaagadasa; ‘Intte laattanau geliyo biittai he biittan de7iya asaa tunatettaappe denddidaagan tuniis; ha gaxaappe biidi, hini gaxaa gakkanaashin, eti a bantta tuna oosuwan kunttidosona.  
\v 12 Hegaa gishshau, intte mino gidana mala, he biittaa aifiyaa maana malanne merinau intte naatussi laatissana mala, intte macca naata eta attuma naatuyyo immoppite; eta macca naatakka intte attuma naatuyyo ekkoppite. Eti sarotettaaninne duretettan de7ana malakka amottoppite’ yaagadasa.   
\p
\v 13 “Nu bolli gakkida iitabai ubbai nu iita oosuwaappenne nu gita naaquwaappe denddidaagaana. Gidikkonne, neeni nu Xoossai nu nagaraa daruwaa keenaa nuna pirddabaakka; shin nuuppe amaridaageeta zerettau palahissadasa.  
\v 14 Yaatin, nuuni ha77ikka zaarettidi, hagaa mala tunabaa oottiya asatuura imuwaaninne ehuwan walahettidi, ne azazuwaa ixxisi gaanee? Qassi ha attida guutta zerettatikka xayana gakkanaashin, ne hanqqoi nu bollan darenneeyye?  
\v 15 Abeet GODAU, Israa7eela Xoossau, neeni xillo. Nu naaquwaappe denddidaagan nuuppe issoinne ne sinttan eqqanau danddayennaagaa gidikkonne, nuuni zerettau palahidi attidaageeti hachchi hagan ne sinttan de7oos” yaagaas.   
\c 10  
\s1 Aihudati Aihuda Gidennaageetuppe Ekkido Machchota Yedissanau Kessido Halchchuwaa  
\p
\v 1 Iziri Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa sinttan kunddidi yeekkiiddi woossiyo wodenne nagaraakka paaxiyo wode, Israa7eela asaappe daroi, maccai, attumainne naatoi ubbai akko shiiqidi, misho yeehuwaa aara yeekkidosona.  
\v 2 Hegaappe guyyiyan, Elaama yara gidiya Yihi7eela na7ai SHakaanee hagaadan yaagiis; “Nuuni ha biittan de7iya Aihuda gidenna maccaasata machchido gishshau, nu Xoossaassi ammanettibookko. Gidikkonne, qassi Israa7eelassi ha77ikka hidootai de7ees.  
\v 3 Hegaa gishshau ta godau, neeninne nu Xoossaa azazuwaassi yayyiyaageeti zoridoogaadan nuuni ha maccaasatanne etappe yelettida naata ubbaa yeddanau nu Xoossaara maacettoos. Hagee ubbai higgee giyoogaadan poletto.  
\v 4 Ha yohuwaa nuuni waati oottanaakko, nuna kaalettanaagee ne ooso gidiyo gishshau, dendda! Minna! Nuunikka nena maaddana” yaagiis.   
\p
\v 5 Yaagin Iziri denddi eqqidi, halaqata, qeeseta, Leewatanne Israa7eela asaa ubbaa ha geetettidaagaadan oottana mala caaqissiis; etikka caaqqidosona.  
\v 6 Hegaappe guyyiyan, Iziri Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa sinttaappe denddidi, Eliyaashiba na7ai Yahohanaani de7iyo kifiliyaa geliis. Gelidi kumetta qammaa omooduwaappe simmida asatu nagaraassi yeekkiiddi aqido gishshau, he sohuwan qumaa mibeenna; haattaakka uyibeenna.   
\p
\v 7 Hegaappe guyyiyan, omooduwaappe simmida asai ubbai Yerusalaame shiiqana mala, Yihudaa ubbaaninne Yerusalaamen awaajuwaa awaajjidosona.  
\v 8 Ha heezzu gallassatu giddon he sohuwaa shiiqenna ooninne de7ikko, au de7iyaabai ubbai appe ekettanaadaaninne ikka omooduwaappe simmida galchchaappe shaahettidi yedetettanaadan halaqatinne cimati kuuyidosona.   
\p
\v 9 He geetettida heezzu gallassati wurennan de7ishin, uddufuntta aginan laatamantta gallassan Yihudaanne Biniyaama asai ubbai Yerusalaame shiiqidosona; shiiqidi, ha deexo yohuwaappenne wolqqaama iraappe denddidaagan kokkoriiddi, Xoossaa Beeta Maqidasiyaa sinttan de7iya dabaaban uttidosona.  
\v 10 Uttidaashin qeesee Iziri denddi eqqidi, eta hagaadan yaagiis; “Aihuda gidenna maccaasatuppe machchota ekkidi naaqqideta; he gaasuwan Israa7eela asaa naaquwaa kaseegaappekka yaa darissideta.  
\v 11 Ha77i intte nagaraa GODAASSI, intte maizza aawatu Xoossaassi paaxite; i dosiyoobaakka oottite. He biittan de7iya Aihuda gidenna asatuppenne Aihuda gidenna intte machchetuppe shaahettite” yaagiis.   
\p
\v 12 Yaagin he sohuwan shiiqida galchchai bantta cenggurssaa xoqqu oottidi, hagaadan yaagidosona; “Neeni nuuyyo yootidoogaadan nuuni oottanau bessees.  
\v 13 SHin asaa qoodai cora; irainne wolqqaamidi bukkees. Yaaniyo gishshau, nuuni iraappe attiyoosi bainna sohuwan hagan eqqi agganau danddayokko. Qassi nuuni ha yohuwan keehippe naaqqido gishshau, hagee issi gallassan woi naa77u gallassan giigiyaabaa gidenna.  
\v 14 Hegaa gishshau, ha shiiqida asaa sunttan nu halaqati Yerusalaamen takkidi, koshshiyaabaa oottona. Ha yohuwaappe denddidaagan Xoossaa wolqqaama hanqqoi nuuppe simmana gakkanaashin, nu katamatun de7iya Aihuda gidenna maccaasata machchida ubbai keerido wodiyan Yerusalaame yona; qassi he katamatu cimatinne pirddiyaageetikka etaara yona” yaagidosona.  
\v 15 Asaaheela na7ai Yonaataaninne Tiiqiwa na7ai Yaahizaayi eta qofaa phalqqidosona; qassi Mashulaaminne Leewa gidiya SHabbataayi phalqqiyaageeta maaddidosona.   
\p
\v 16 Hegaa gishshau, omooduwaappe simmida asai he giidoogaadan oottidosona. Qeesee Iziri ubba zaretuppekka halaqata dooridi, ubbaakka eta sunttan sunttan xaafiis. Tammantta aginan koiro gallassan halaqati yohuwaa qori xeellanau doommidosona.  
\v 17 Koiro aginan koiro gallassai gakkiyo wode, Aihuda gidenna maccaasata machchida asata ubbaa qoridi wurssidosona.   
\s1 Aihuda Gidenna Maccaasatuppe Machcho Ekkida Asaa Sunttaa  
\p
\v 18 Aihuda gidenna maccaasatuppe machcho ekkidaageeti hagaappe kaallidi xaafettidaageeta.  
\p Qeesetuppe: Yoxedeeqa naata gidiya Yaasunne a ishanttu yaraappe Ma7iseeya, El77eezara, Yaariibanne Gadaaliyaa.  
\v 19 Hageeti bantta Aihuda gidenna machchota yeddanau caaqqidosona; qassi bantta naaquwaa gishshau, wudiyaappe issi dorssa orggiyaa naaquwaa yarshsho oottidi yarshshidosona.  
\v 20 Imeera yaran Aihuda gidenna machchota ekkidaageeti Hanaananne Zabaadiyaa.  
\v 21 Hariima yaratuppe Ma7iseeya, Eelaasa, SHamaa7iyaa, Yihi7eelanne Ooziyaana.  
\v 22 Paashihuura yaratuppe Eliyoo7enaaya, Ma7iseeya, Isimaa7eela, Nataani7eela, Yozabaadanne El77aasa.   
\p
\v 23 Leewatuppe: Yozabaada, SHamaa7iyaa, Qaliixa giyo Qelaaya, Pataahiyaa, Yihudaanne El77eezara.   
\p
\v 24 Mazamuriyaa yexxiyaageetuppe: Eliyaashiba.  
\p Penggiyaa naagiyaageetuppe: SHaaluuma, Xelemanne Uura.   
\p
\v 25 Qassi hara Israa7eela asaappe: Par77oosha yaratuppe Raamiyaa, Yizziyaa, Malkkiyaa, Miyaamiina, El77aazara, Malkkiyaanne Banaaya.   
\p
\v 26 Elaama yaratuppe Mataaniyaa, Zakkaariyaasa, Yihi7eela, Abdda, Yiremootanne Eelaasa.   
\p
\v 27 Zattu yaratuppe Eliyoo7enaaya, Eliyaashiba, Mataaniyaa, Yiremoota, Zabaadanne Aziiza.   
\p
\v 28 Bebaaya yaratuppe Yahohanaana, Hanaaniyaa, Zabbaayanne Atilaaya.   
\p
\v 29 Baana yaratuppe Mashulaama, Malluuka, Adaaya, Yaashuuba, SHa7aalanne Yiremoota.   
\p
\v 30 Paahati-Moo7aaba yaratuppe Adinaaha, Kalaala, Banaaya, Ma7iseeya, Mataaniyaa, Baxaali7eela, Biinuyanne Minaasa.   
\p
\v 31 Hariima yaratuppe El77eezara, Yishiyaa, Malkkiyaa, SHamaa7iyaa, SHim77oona,  
\v 32 Biniyaama, Malluukanne SHamaariyaa.   
\p
\v 33 Hashuuma yaratuppe Matanaaya, Mataata, Zabaada, Elifeleexa, Yeremaaya, Minaasanne SHim77a.   
\p
\v 34 Baana yaratuppe Ma7idaaya, Amiraama, U7eela,  
\v 35 Banaaya, Bediyaa, Kaluuha,  
\v 36 Waaniyaa, Maremoota, Eliyaashiba,  
\v 37 Mataaniyaa Matanaayanne Yaa7isa.   
\p
\v 38 Biinuya yaratuppe SHim77a,  
\v 39 SHeleemiyaa, Naataana, Adaaya,  
\v 40 Makinadabaaya, SHashaaya, SHaraaya,  
\v 41 Azaari7eela, SHeleemiyaa, SHamaariyaa,  
\v 42 SHaaluuma, Amaariyaanne Yooseefa.   
\p
\v 43 Nabo yaratuppe Yi7i7eela, Matiitiyaa, Zabaada, Zabiina, Yaddaaya, Yuu7eelanne Banaaya.   
\p
\v 44 Hageeti ubbati Aihuda gidenna machchota machchidaageeta. Issooti issooti harai atto naatakka yelidosona.   